		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you disable rendering (lda #0 sta $2001) for too long, it'll <em>overwrite</em> the palette and OAM with random data, but it doesn't permanently <em>damage</em> anything.
<br />
<br />A "dumb question" is a question whose answer all people in the discussion should already know. But here, we prefer the traditional meaning of "dumb" (that is, not speaking), and the only dumb question is the one that you don't ask.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
